  "prompt": "Which is the best immigration consultancy in India?",
  "response": "Determining the \"best\" immigration consultancy in India can be subjective, as it often depends on individual needs, experiences, and specific immigration goals. However, several well-known immigration consultancies have established good reputations based on customer reviews, success rates, and services offered. Some of the prominent immigration consultancies in India include:\n\n1. **Visas Avenue** - Known for its comprehensive services in Canada and Australia immigration.\n2. **Y-Axis** - One of the leading immigration consultants with a wide range of services for various countries.\n3. **Global Tree** - Offers services for multiple immigration pathways, including study, work, and permanent residency.\n4. **Abhinav Immigration Services** - Offers guidance on multiple immigration programs, particularly for Canada and Australia.\n5. **Nationwide Visas** - Known for providing personalized immigration solutions and guidance.\n\nBefore choosing an immigration consultancy, it\u2019s advisable to do thorough research, check reviews, compare services, and consult with multiple providers to find one that aligns with your specific needs. Always ensure that the consultancy is registered and has a good track record.",
